title: XCOM 2 War of the Chosen-CODEX
description:
XCOM 2: War of the Chosen,  is the  expansion to  the  2016  award-
      winning strategy game of the year. XCOM 2: War  of  the  Chosenadds
      extensive new content in the fight against ADVENT  when  additional
      resistance factions form in order to eliminate the alien  threat on
      Earth. In response, a new enemy, known as the Chosen,  emerges with
      one goal: recapture the Commander.

      For more info go to : http://store.steampowered.com/app/593380/
